name: TD Global Technology Leaders CAD Hedged Index ETF
longDescription: TD ETF seeks to track the Solactive Global Technology Leaders Hedged to CAD Index (CA NTR) (or any successor thereto), an index calculated by Solactive AG which tracks the performance of securities of global mid- and large-capitalization issuers that are related to technology, while hedging Canadian dollar risk, but not the underlying equity market risk. This ETF invest in and hold a proportionate share or a sampling of constituent securities of the index to seek to track the performance of that index.
fulldescription: TD ETF seeks to track the Solactive Global Technology Leaders Hedged to CAD Index (CA NTR) (or any successor thereto), an index calculated by Solactive AG which tracks the performance of securities of global mid- and large-capitalization issuers that are related to technology, while hedging Canadian dollar risk, but not the underlying equity market risk. This ETF invest in and hold a proportionate share or a sampling of constituent securities of the index to seek to track the performance of that index. As an alternative to or in conjunction with investing in and holding the constituent securities, the ETF may also invest in other securities to obtain exposure to the constituent securities of the index in a manner that is consistent with the investment objectives of the ETF.
